race.description: Rjc Raceday Thursday 18 Dec Maiden Plate
race.comment: SHE'S GOT LYRICS (9) has had a few chances but has placed over this track and trip and will be rock-hard fit for this. Looks ready to break the maiden status against this line-up. The well-related GALVANIZE (3) (half to G3 winner Extreme Warrior) is facing the starter for the first time but has been thereabouts in both trials and gets Wiggins on board from a favourable draw. Any market confidence must be noted. CASH PIT (1) has placed three of six here on his home circuit and must be included in the exotics. Former Victorian SKILFUL ARTIST (4) just ran into one better when having the first run for the new stable and will have come on with that run now in the locker. In the mix. ATLANTIC LACE (8) rounds out the selections in a race with only a handful of hopes.
